types.html:
ravioli chinois m (plural raviolis chinois)

  1. any small pasta-sheet wrapped Chinese food, Chinese dumplings such as potstickers, wontons, shumai, har gow, etc, frequently found in dim sum
trans: any small pasta-sheet wrapped Chinese food, Chinese dumplings such as potstickers, wontons, shumai, har gow, etc, frequently found in dim sum
